# Website Theme — LOCKED

This theme is final. All future changes MUST follow it exactly. Do NOT deviate.

## Color Palette (solid colors only, NO gradients)

- **Primary blue**: `#1d4ed8` / `blue-700` (buttons, headers, links, stats)
- **Accent orange**: `#ea580c` / `orange-500`–`orange-600` (highlights, NEW badges, featured CTAs)
- **White**: `#ffffff` (main section backgrounds)
- **Light gray**: `slate-50` (alternate section backgrounds)
- **Dark**: `slate-900` (hero, dark sections, footer)
- **Text**: `slate-900` headings, `slate-600` body, `slate-400`/`slate-500` secondary
- **Emerald** `emerald-600` WhatsApp buttons only

## Design Rules

- NO gradients on backgrounds, buttons, or text — use solid flat colors
- NO glassmorphism, shimmer, glow, blur, or animated color effects
- NO fancy AI-looking effects — keep it looking human-made and professional
- Borders: `border-slate-200` (light sections), `border-slate-700` (dark sections)
- Border radius: `rounded-lg` (10px) on cards, panels, buttons
- Card hover: `translateY(-2px)` + subtle `box-shadow` only
- Panels: white bg, `1px solid #e2e8f0`, `rounded-lg`
- Buttons: solid bg color, `rounded-lg`, `font-semibold`, simple `hover:` darken

## Typography

- Display font: `Libre Baskerville` via `font-display` (headings)
- Body font: `Source Sans 3` via `font-sans`
- Headings: `font-bold text-slate-900`
- Tags/labels: `text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-700` or `text-orange-600`

## Component Patterns

- Section spacing: `py-24 md:py-28`
- Max width: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6`
- Badges: solid bg (`bg-orange-500`, `bg-red-600`), white text, `rounded`, `uppercase`, `font-bold`
- CTA buttons: `bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800` primary, `bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600` accent
- Outline buttons: `border-2 border-slate-300 text-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500`
